1073742126::Name: EMPLOYEE
1073742125::Definition: EMPLOYEE is a person that works for the VIDEO STORE

1073742126::Name: MOVIE
1073742125::Definition: A MOVIE is any video that can be rented” for the entity “MOVIE

1073742126::Name: STORE
1073742125::Definition: A STORE is one of the MOVIE STORES where a customer can rent a movie

1073742126::Name: MOVIE RENTAL RECORD
1073742125::Definition: A MOVIE RENTAL RECORD is a record that  is kept on every MOVIE in the STORE  on who and when a MOVIE is rented

1073742126::Name: MOVIE COPY
1073742125::Definition: A MOVIE COPY is a single copy of a MOVIE

1073742126::Name: CUSTOMER
1073742125::Definition: A CUSTOMER is a person or organization who has rented a movie within the past year.

1073742126::Name: CUSTOMER CREDIT
1073742125::Definition: CUSTOMER CREDIT is the status of available credit for a CUSTOMER

1073742126::Name: PAYMENT
1073742125::Definition: A PAYMENT is received when a customer rents a movie
